entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have done what few non-Selonians have ever done. Earned the title of den mate.
entries.journal_entry_description: You have been asked to speak to the den mother, the matriarch of this den of Selonians.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Go to the bottom of the Selonian cave and speak with the matriarch of the den.
